() 30-day boundary check** (`src/orders/service.ts:95`)\n- `if (daysSinceCreation >= REFUND_WINDOW_DAYS)` — should be `>` (strictly greater than)\n- Day 30 should still be refundable\n\nNow let me fix them all:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":400,"cache_read_input_tokens":36456,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":400},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f32b9cf4-cab9-497d-ad69-77b317355e84","uuid":"86bd11ce-4b00-4cf1-8dd1-a78609e6958d"}
